x200m freestyle relay and bronze in the 400m freestyle in Paris.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.067813775823421e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The greatest distance\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1500m\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x200m freestyle relay\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m freestyle\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No other woman swimmer has won gold at four different Olympics and Ledecky said that was the record that gave her particular satisfaction.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No other woman swimmer\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"four different Olympics\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"her particular satisfaction\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think four times one is the one that kind of means the most to me.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like I put a lot of pressure on myself but I am just really happy that I could get the job done,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\":